title: The Allman Brothers Band - Live At Ludlow Garage 1970 [320k MP3]
description:
Live at Ludlow Garage: 1970 is an album by The Allman Brothers Band. It was recorded live at Ludlow Garage in Cincinnati in April 1970. It was released by Polydor Records on April 20, 1990.

The album is noted for having the longest recorded version of "Mountain Jam", at 44 minutes.

Track Listing [320k MP3]

    "Dreams" (Allman) - 10:15
    "Statesboro Blues" (McTell) - 8:09
    "Trouble No More" (Morganfield) - 4:13
    "Dimples" (Bracken/Hooker) - 5:00
    "Every Hungry Woman" (Allman) - 4:28
    "I'm Gonna Move to the Outskirts of Town" (Weldon) - 9:22
    "Hoochie Coochie Man" (Dixon) - 5:23
    "Mountain Jam"  - 44:00
